---
<BaseLayout
  title="Restaurant Website Design Maryland | Upcoming Brand"
  description="WordPress website design for Maryland restaurants. Restaurant schema, OpenTable integration, online ordering, and 90+ PageSpeed. Fixed-scope from $1,500. Serving Baltimore."
  canonicalUrl="https://upcomingbrand.com/industries/restaurant-website-design/"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} slot="head" />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lfh-hero">

    <div class="container">
      <nav class="lfh-breadcrumb mono-xs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="/#industries">Industries</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>Restaurant Website Design</span>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container lfh-wrap">

      <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
      <div class="lfh-left">

        <div class="lfh-tags">
          <span class="lfh-pill">
            <span class="lfh-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Restaurant Web Design &middot; Maryland
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-sep" aria-hidden="true">/</span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-eyebrow">A specialist studio, not a template shop</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="lfh-h1">
          <span class="lfh-h1-line">Maryland restaurant websites</span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-accent-line"><em class="lfh-h1-accent">built to fill tables</em></span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-italic">and drive reservations.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="lfh-lede">
          Most restaurant websites lose diners before they make a reservation: outdated menus, no online booking, and sites that load in 8 seconds on mobile. We build WordPress sites for Maryland restaurants that rank locally, integrate with OpenTable or Resy, and turn visitors into regulars. Fixed-scope from <strong>$1,500</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="lfh-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="lfh-btn-primary">
            Book a discovery call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="lfh-btn-ghost">
            See pricing
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 12L12 2M12 2H5M12 2v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="lfh-trust">
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.35"/><path d="M3.5 6l2 2 3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Maryland-based studio
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Restaurant schema on every build</span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Fixed-scope &middot; no surprises</span>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: FORM -->
      <div class="lfh-right">
        <div class="lfh-form-card">
          <div class="lfh-form-header">
            <p class="lfh-form-eyebrow">Free site audit</p>
            <h2 class="lfh-form-title">Is your website costing you covers?</h2>
            <p class="lfh-form-sub">We review your current site and send a plain-English audit within 2 business days. No sales call required.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="lfh-form" name="restaurant-inquiry" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" data-netlify="true" action="/thank-you/">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="restaurant-inquiry" />
            <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
              <label>Leave blank: <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="rst-name">Your name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="rst-name" name="name" placeholder="James Whitfield" required autocomplete="name" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="rst-email">Email address</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="email" id="rst-email" name="email" placeholder="james@annapolisoysterhouse.com" required autocomplete="email" />
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="rst-restaurant">Restaurant name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="rst-restaurant" name="restaurant" placeholder="Annapolis Oyster House" autocomplete="organization" />
            </div>

